description	"Jedi Wookiee

^2Weaponry:
- Melee
- Lighsaber
-- ^1Red ^7Style Only
-- Saber Defense (3)
-- Blaster Defense / Deflect (2)
-- Attack-Defense (Q3)

^5Force Powers:
- Jump  (3)
- Push  (2)
- Pull  (2)
- Speed (3)
- Heal  (2)
- Blinding (1)

^8Attributes:
- BP Free Jumps
- Strength (2)
- Force Block / Focus (1)

Whilst Han Solo was making preparations to go into combat with the local imperial garrison, a Wookiee was watching him, not just any Wookiee, a skilled Jedi Wookiee.
During the battle Han Solo was ambushed by the Jedi Wookiee, and then the Wookiee attacked him by means of a friendly hug and a loud friendly roar in his ears, which of course, Han Solo enjoyed with much regret..
Han Solo, being deafened by the roar, didn't realise the Wookiee was a Jedi, but when finally freed from a vice-like grip and was told, he welcomed the Wookiee into his attack group, whilst rubbing his ribs."